'''艾琳·伊蕾兒·莫里亞蒂'''（{{lang-en|'''Erin Elair Moriarty'''}}，{{bd|1994年|6月24日||}}）<!--BDay a little in question because http://www.teenvogue.com/entertainment/movies/2013-02/toys-house-erin-moriarty-interview implies ''[[The_Kings_of_Summer|The Kings of Summer]]'' started filming before her 15th BDay in 2009--><ref name=EMM/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.whowhatwear.com/meet-actress-erin-moriartyour-favorite-fresh-new-face/|title=Get To Know Actress Erin Moriarty--Our Favorite Fresh New Face|accessdate=November 26, 2013|date=March 20, 2013|work=WhoWhatWear.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202232449/http://www.whowhatwear.com/meet-actress-erin-moriartyour-favorite-fresh-new-face/|archive-date=2013-12-02}}</ref>是一位[[美國|美國]][[女演員|女演員]]。她在電視劇《[[只此一生|只此一生]]》以及《[[無間警探|無間警探]]》中演出常設角色，並在《[[血玫瑰_(美國電視劇)|血玫瑰]]》、《[[潔西卡·瓊斯_(電視劇)|潔西卡·瓊斯]]》飾演常規角色，並在數部電影中演出配角。{{As of|2019}}，莫里亞蒂在亞馬遜旗下[[Prime_Video|Prime Video]]基於同名漫畫系列的原創影集《[[黑袍糾察隊_(電視劇)|黑袍糾察隊]]》中演出女主角[[星光_(角色)|安妮·詹紐瑞／星光]]。

==早年生活==
她在[[紐約州|紐約州]][[紐約市|紐約市]]出生並成長。<ref name=EMoSiSFTH>{{cite web|url=http://www.teenvogue.com/entertainment/movies/2013-02/toys-house-erin-moriarty-interview|title=Erin Moriarty on Starring in Sundance Favorite 'Toy's House'|accessdate=November 26, 2013|date=February 2013|work=[[Teen_Vogue|Teen Vogue]]|author=Mathews, Dana|archive-date=2013-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202235400/http://www.teenvogue.com/entertainment/movies/2013-02/toys-house-erin-moriarty-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref>莫里亞蒂在11歲開始演戲，在2005年時於[[社區劇場|社區劇場]]製作的音樂劇《[[安妮得到你的槍|安妮得到你的槍]]》中主演安妮。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.offoffonline.com/archives.php?id=558|title=Evergreen|last=Strassler|first=Doug|date=November 18, 2005|website=Off Off Online|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111010052546/http://www.offoffonline.com/archives.php?id=558|archive-date=October 10, 2011|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sites.google.com/site/stjeansplayers/photos-of-past-productions/annie|title=Annie - St. Jean's Players|last=|first=|date=|website=St. Jeans Players|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603122844/https://sites.google.com/site/stjeansplayers/photos-of-past-productions/annie|archive-date=2016-06-03|access-date=2020-02-29|quote=and Erin Moriarty as Annie.|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在高中畢業後，她為了演戲而推遲進入大學。<ref name=EMoSiSFTH/>

==職業生活==
