Justin|archive-date=2014-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140311015225/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/true-detectiver-erin-moriarty-new-lines-crawlspace-1201128737/|dead-url=no}}</ref>為[[伍迪·哈里遜|伍迪·哈里遜]]飾演角色的問題女兒。<ref name=EM&DYTOISMLLL/>她隨後出現在2016年[[梅爾·吉勃遜|梅爾·吉勃遜]]主演的電影《[[吾父吾血|吾父吾血]]》 中。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2014/film/news/erin-moriarty-mel-gibson-in-bloodfather-1201163464/ |title=Erin Moriarty to Co-Star With Mel Gibson in Blood Father |publisher=Variety |date=April 24, 2014 |accessdate=June 6, 2014 |archive-date=2014-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140501021501/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/erin-moriarty-mel-gibson-in-bloodfather-1201163464/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>她在《吾父吾血》中飾演吉勃遜的女兒一角獲得包含《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的[[瑪諾拉·達吉斯|瑪諾拉·達吉斯]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/26/movies/blood-father-review-mel-gibson.html|title=Review: In ‘Blood Father,’ Mel Gibson Plays With Pulp Fiction|accessdate=2016-10-16|date=2016-08-25|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|author=Dargis, Manohla|archive-date=2016-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826094149/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/26/movies/blood-father-review-mel-gibson.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、《[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]》的[[艾隆索·杜拉德|艾隆索·杜拉德]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thewrap.com/blood-father-review/|title=‘Blood Father’ Karlovy Vary Review: Mel Gibson Strikes Grindhouse Gold|accessdate=2016-10-16|date=2016-07-02|publisher=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]|author=Duralde, Alonso|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108125253/https://www.thewrap.com/blood-father-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》的[[歐文·葛列伯曼|歐文·葛列伯曼]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2016/film/festivals/cannes-mel-gibson-blood-father-1201780294/|title=Cannes Film Review: ‘Blood Father’|accessdate=2016-10-16|date=2016-05-21|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|author=Gleiberman, Owen|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108112924/https://variety.com/2016/film/festivals/cannes-mel-gibson-blood-father-1201780294/|dead-url=no}}</ref>等影評人讚美，但[[The_A.V._Club|The A.V. Club]]的[[伊格納帝·文西涅夫茲基|伊格納帝·文西涅夫茲基]]認為她的表演不令人信服。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.avclub.com/review/mel-gibson-attempts-action-comedy-comeback-blood-f-240937|title=Mel Gibson attempts an action-comedy comeback in Blood Father|accessdate=2016-10-16|date=2016-08-11|work=[[The_A.V._Club|The A.V. Club]]|author=Vishnevetsky, Ignatiy|archive-date=2017-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170128211458/http://www.avclub.com/review/mel-gibson-attempts-action-comedy-comeback-blood-f-240937|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[紐約每日新聞|紐約每日新聞]]》的[[艾倫·沙爾金|艾倫·沙爾金]]則認為她的表現被吉勃遜以及[[威廉·梅西|威廉·梅西]]所獲得的喜愛所掩蓋。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/mel-gibson-returns-leading-man-form-blood-father-review-article-1.2758205|title=Mel Gibson returns in 'Blood Father' with chance for another ride through revenge thriller genre: movie review|accessdate=2016-10-16|date=2016-08-19|work=[[New_York_Daily_News|New York Daily News]]|author=Salkin, Allen|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107023359/https://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/mel-gibson-returns-leading-man-form-blood-father-review-article-1.2758205|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年9月，艾琳·莫里亞蒂被《[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]》認為是21世紀中其中一名最好的20歲以下女演員。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Staff|first1=The Playlist|title=On The Rise: 20 Actors To Watch That Are Under 20|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2014/09/on-the-rise-20-actors-to-watch-that-are-under-20-272876/|website=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|accessdate=February 16, 2017|archive-date=2018-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630000232/https://www.indiewire.com/2014/09/on-the-rise-20-actors-to-watch-that-are-under-20-272876/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在《[[神奇大隊長|神奇大隊長]]》中，她飾演[[乔治·麦凯_(演员)|喬治·麥凱]]演出角色的戀愛對象。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://time.com/4379475/father-doesnt-always-know-best-in-captain-fantastic/|title=Father Doesn’t Always Know Best In Captain Fantastic|accessdate=2016-10-16|date=2016-06-23|work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]]|author=Zacharek, Stephanie|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108134339/https://time.com/4379475/father-doesnt-always-know-best-in-captain-fantastic/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在《[[潔西卡·瓊斯_(電視劇)|潔西卡·瓊斯]]》第一季中，莫里亞蒂飾演一名生活困難的大學生。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bustle.com/articles/125455-who-is-hope-shlottman-on-jessica-jones-erin-moriarty-gives-our-hero-a-new-mission|title=Who Is Hope Shlottman On 'Jessica Jones'? Erin Moriarty Gives Our Hero A New Mission|accessdate=2016-10-16|date=2015-11-23|work=[[Bustle_(magazine)|Bustle]]|author=Narasaki, Rosie|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023224309/https://www.bustle.com/articles/125455-who-is-hope-shlottman-on-jessica-jones-erin-moriarty-gives-our-hero-a-new-mission|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年6月，莫里亞蒂在[[LD娛樂|LD娛樂]]出品的電影《[[奇蹟的賽季|奇蹟的賽季]]》與[[達妮卡·亞羅許|達妮卡·亞羅許]]及[[海倫·杭特|海倫·杭特]]一同演出。<ref name=EM&DYTOISMLLL>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2016/06/erin-moriarty-danika-yarosh-live-like-line-movie-hiroyuki-sanad-sony-movie-life-1201778526/|title=Erin Moriarty & Danika Yarosh Team On Inspirational Sports Movie ‘Live Like Line’|accessdate=2016-10-16|date=2016-06-23|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|author=Busch, Anita|archive-date=2016-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624094817/https://deadline.com/2016/06/erin-moriarty-danika-yarosh-live-like-line-movie-hiroyuki-sanad-sony-movie-life-1201778526/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年12月，她在[[亞馬遜工作室|亞馬遜工作室]]出品，由[[蓋斯·恩尼斯|蓋斯·恩尼斯]]與[[德瑞克·羅伯森|德瑞克·羅伯森]]原著的同名漫畫改編影集《[[黑袍糾察隊_(電視劇)|黑袍糾察隊]]》出演女主角[[星光_(角色)|安妮·詹紐瑞／星光]]<ref name=EM&THEBOYS>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2017/12/the-boys-erin-moriarty-cast-amazon-superhero-drama-series-comic-book-1202229406/|title=‘The Boys’: Erin Moriarty Cast In Amazon’s Superhero Drama Series Based On Comic Book|accessdate=2018-01-18|date=2017-12-18|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|author=Andreeva, Nellie & Petski, Denise|archive-date=2017-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171221001152/https://deadline.com/2017/12/the-boys-erin-moriarty-cast-amazon-superhero-drama-series-comic-book-1202229406/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該影集在2019年7月上架，並已續訂第二季。<ref name="S2Renewal">{{cite web|last=Petski|first=Denise|title='The Boys' Renewed For Season 2 By Amazon; Aya Cash Closes Deal As Stormfront|url=https://deadline.com/2019/07/the-boys-renewed-season-2-amazon-aya-cash-closes-deal-stormfront-1202649409/|website=Deadline Hollywood|accessdate=July 19, 2019|date=July 19, 2019|archive-date=2019-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190719235155/https://deadline.com/2019/07/the-boys-renewed-season-2-amazon-aya-cash-closes-deal-stormfront-1202649409/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年，莫里亞蒂在電影《[[失控|失控]]》中主演，該電影描述扳倒汽車業大人物[[約翰·德羅寧|約翰·德羅寧]]的臥底行動。

